AI Jesse 
AI-Jesse   I've re-created myself as a chatbot. AI-Jesse is a natural language (NLP) chatbot based on chat GPT. The link at the top is code.jessejesse.com. An a.i. enabled code translator that can quickly translate code from one language to another. If promted for a key you can grab an API key from openAI .
